    <abstract>
      <t>This specification defines Simple Phone Control Protocol (SPCP) as an application-level protocol, which allows network devices, such as PCs, to control IP telephones. This document explains the protocol specification, how to use SPCP, and how to configure a system that uses SPCP.</t>
